{"tid":2087901,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Anne Hathaway：Nolan拍攝現場不准人坐凳 導演發言人：並無此事","createTime":"2020-07-01T01:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T06:10:35.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"356fcc8b46c6463e8c6d7da33070e8170bdc9841","tid":2087901,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T01:45:50.000Z","msg":"安海瑟薇失憶or失言？她受訪時大爆導演克里斯多夫諾蘭拍片現場不准出現椅子給人坐；之後立刻遭諾蘭公關發言人出面否認。<br />\n<br />\n美國「紐約郵報」（New York Post）娛樂版Page Six報導：安海瑟薇和休傑克曼接受影視媒體「綜藝報」（Variety）的「星對星」聯訪時，脫口而出：「大導演克里斯多夫諾蘭的拍片現場禁止有椅子！」<br />\n<br />\n「諾蘭禁止在片場有椅子，因為如果有椅子，有人就會坐，有人一坐，就不想工作了。」安海瑟薇說。<br />\n<br />\n安海瑟薇主演過諾蘭執導的《黑暗騎士：黎明昇起》（2012年），《星際效應》（2014年），難道演那2部片時，她都被「罰站」？安海瑟薇沒有再「吐槽」自身遭遇。<br />\n<br />\n不過消息一出立刻引發反彈，諾蘭的公關發言人對另一家影視娛媒「Indie Wire」作出更正聲明表示：「諾蘭先生拍片現場從來沒有禁止擺椅子，演員可以坐在任何他們想坐的地方。」對準安海瑟薇的「無椅說」狠狠打臉。<br />\n<br />\n諾蘭的公關發言人不忘略施「佛心」緩頰：「安海瑟薇提到的『沒有椅子（不准坐）』，可能是在工作人員圍在拍攝鏡頭旁看監控器時的情況吧。」<br />\n<br />\n而趁此機會，諾蘭公關發言人主動爆料：「諾蘭片場禁令沒有禁擺椅子，但禁止帶手機到片場，這禁令不是總能成功；最重要的是嚴禁片場抽菸，此禁令一定要嚴格執行成功。」<br />\n<br />\n諾蘭片場下達禁帶手機、禁菸的命令，合情合理；只是安海瑟薇主動加了「禁椅令」，卻被公關發言人否認；無論事實如何，拍任何導演的戲，即使沒有禁令也要自律，那才是演員與工作人員該有的真正敬業態度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E5%AE%89%E6%B5%B7%E7%91%9F%E8%96%87-%E7%84%A1%E6%A4%85%E8%AA%AA-%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93%E8%87%89-%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E8%AB%BE%E8%98%AD%E7%89%87%E5%A0%B4%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-232604645.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%2591%259F%25E8%2596%2587-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25A4%2585%25E8%25AA%25AA-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%2587%2589-%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%25BC%2594%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E8%2598%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-232604645.html&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=af5f0ebf\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E5%AE%89%E6%B5%B7%E7%91%9F%E8%96%87-%E7%84%A1%E6%A4%85%E8%AA%AA-%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93%E8%87%89-%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E8%AB%BE%E8%98%AD%E7%89%87%E5%A0%B4%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-232604645.html</a>"},{"pid":"ace8c6a80d466dec0695b7af17b7d067525dd31e","tid":2087901,"uid":172677,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T01:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zRSuerS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzRSuerS.jpg&h=f292f933&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2af7a27088405db58f1d76925cec97f51182b6df","tid":2087901,"uid":236359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T01:57:01.000Z","msg":"八卦新聞"},{"pid":"1eaf5388302f01f1e363703fe7e975bc255447ee","tid":2087901,"uid":34572,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3taSWPc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3taSWPc.png&h=a08c2be6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4257ea5764e8b1dce15a696188f2aa1a36b6fe55","tid":2087901,"uid":4574,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:22:37.000Z","msg":"Nolan拍唔拍到 香港嘅荒謬"},{"pid":"745210ea194b136b5f91862b532d28a2844ad47a","tid":2087901,"uid":42848,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:33:57.000Z","msg":"最重要的是嚴禁片場抽菸，此禁令一定要嚴格執行成功<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2660fdac3e1939ce39a47d69fa51693c3c3964c","tid":2087901,"uid":206557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ace8c6a80d466dec0695b7af17b7d067525dd31e","tid":2087901,"uid":172677,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T01:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zRSuerS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzRSuerS.jpg&h=f292f933&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:51:00.000Z","msg":"拍天能？"},